<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-54-1272 </DOCNO><TEXT>VEGIN (Association of Proprietors of Gas Companies in the Netherlands)will shortly complete a plan for the marketing of gas in the commercialsector in the Netherlands. In order to be able to implement the planthe gas industry should know the image of gas and the gas companies heldby the commercial consumers as well as their wishes and needs. The resultsof a study into these aspects are reported. 10 figs., 9 tabs.</TEXT></DOC>